      <h2>CLIENT TRAVEL CONSENT AND RELEASE OF MEDDISTANT INC.</h2>
      <p>This Client Informed Travel Consent and Release (this “Release”) is effective ____________, 20__ ("Effective Date"), between Meddistant Inc. (Referred to as “Company”), an Illinois corporation ("Company"), and ___________________, ("Client") each a “Party” and together, the "Parties."</p>
       <h2>CLIENT RESPONSIBILITY</h2>


